texts.text:
Achievements#Enchanter, a Bedrock Edition achievement obtained by crafting an enchantment table
Advancements#Enchanter, a Java Edition advancement obtained by enchanting an item

Enchanter, an illager that use spells to turn enemies into enchanted mobs.
Enchanter's Tome, an artifact used by Enchanters and used to enchant pets, summoned allied mobs, and players, that was added along with the Gracefully Dangerous Mountains known as the Howling Peaks.
